        "subject": "LU-6225 test: test-framework does not cleanup for failed tests",
        "message": "LU-6225 test: test-framework does not cleanup for failed tests\n\nadding Reset_fail_loc to error() func in test-framework which\nresets fail_loc value to 0 makes sure that the next test will\nbe started with no error injected.\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-2079\n\nSigned-off-by: gaurav mahajan <gaurav.mahajan@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: I8cadd21a794d0eb429aee4734d47bd56caf0b8fe"
